        {
            "title": "天鴿互動去年盈轉虧 全年經調整虧損1246.5萬元人幣 維持每股末期息2港仙",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">天鴿互動(01980)公布2025年度業績，由盈轉虧，按非國際財務報告準則計量，錄得經調整虧損1246.5萬元(人民幣‧下同)。董事會維持擬派末期息每股2港仙。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"天鴿互動2024年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/01980-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"天鴿互動2024年度中期報告封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/01980-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">天鴿互動2024年度中期報告封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內經調整EBITDA亦錄得虧損1423.9萬元。若按國際財報準則，該公司去年錄得虧損1329.6元，收益3855.4萬元，按年則升2.79倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15811489-%e5%a4%a9%e9%b4%bf%e4%ba%92%e5%8b%95%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%9b%88%e8%bd%89%e8%99%a7-%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d1246-5%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3-%e7%b6%ad",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/01980.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 12:38:19",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "雅迪年度利潤增近129%  末期息增1.41倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">雅迪集團(01585)公布，截至2025年12月31日止年度，公司擁有人應佔利潤增加約128.8%至2911.6百萬元(人民幣‧下同)，每股基本盈利增加約127%至95.8分，擬派2025年末期股息每股普通股53仙，較2024年同期每股22港仙增1.41倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/746x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI__1585_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司中期報告封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/746x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI__1585_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司中期報告封面</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">收入增加約31.1%至370.08億元。公布稱，收入增加主要是由於(i)有利的市場情緒與政府政策推動的需求帶動銷售量上升，(ii)集團產品組合的持續優化，及(iii)對研發、營銷及品牌建設舉措的投資增加帶來的正面效果。電動踏板車及電動自行車的總銷量從2024年的約1300萬台增至2025年的約1630萬台。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">毛利率則由2024年約15.2%增加約25.7%至2025年的約19.1%，主要是 由於優化產品組合以滿足不同客戶群以及垂直融合供應鏈所致。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15811487-%e9%9b%85%e8%bf%aa%e5%b9%b4%e5%ba%a6%e5%88%a9%e6%bd%a4%e5%a2%9e%e8%bf%91129-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e5%a2%9e1-41%e5%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/01585-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 12:38:19",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大新金融去年純利增22.9% 同系大新銀行多賺20.2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大新金融(00440)與同系大新銀行(02356)齊於中午公布2025年度業績，純利均按年升逾20%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-web_02356-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240624_FI_source-web_02356-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其中大新金融去年股東應佔溢利20.57億元，增長22.9%。擬派末期息每股1.42元，連同已派中期息每股1.16元，全年每股共派2.58元，較2024年度的2.1元提升22.9%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大新銀行去年股東應佔溢利則為24.76億元，按年增長20.2%。期內淨利息收入58.29億元，升10.2%；淨服務費及佣金收入17.02億元，增長28.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會擬派末期息每股0.49元，計連同已派中期息每股0.31元，全年每股共派0.8元，較2024年度的0.66元提升21.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15811425-%e5%a4%a7%e6%96%b0%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e22-9-%e5%90%8c%e7%b3%bb%e5%a4%a7%e6%96%b0%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c%e5%a4%9a%e8%b3%ba20-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508020_FI_source-web_00440.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 12:31:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "申洲國際稅後淨利跌6.7%  末期息減6.25%全年增約2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">申洲國際(02313)公布，截至2025年12月31日止年度的稅後淨利潤約為58.25億(人民幣‧下同)，按年跌6.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">宣派末期股息每股普通股1.2元，較2024同期1.28元跌6.25%，連同已派發的中期股息每股1.38元，2025年全年建議派發股息合共每股2.58元，比2024每股2.53元上升約2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"申洲國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1119x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02313_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"申洲國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1119x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02313_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">申洲國際官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">銷售額309.94億元，比2024年度上升約8.1%。運動類產品銷售額佔比67.7%，銷售額比2024年度上升約5.9% ; 休閒類產品銷售額佔比約為27.1%，銷售額比2024年度升約16.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公布稱，本年度稅後淨利下跌原因包括︰1）上年度之稅後淨利中包含轉讓集團一家全資附屬公司之股權，取得收益約3.31億元；2）2025年人民幣兌美元匯率上升，導致匯兌虧損約2.56億元人民幣（2024年︰匯兌收益約1.06億元人民幣）。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15811421-%e7%94%b3%e6%b4%b2%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e7%a8%85%e5%be%8c%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c6-7-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%b8%9b6-25%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e7%b4%842",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/02313-2024.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 12:26:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱跌幅收窄 恒指跌224點報24727點 鋁業板塊炒上",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中東戰火持續，港股今早跟隨外圍股市下滑，但跌幅在期指結算前略為收窄，鋁業板塊更明顯炒上，中國宏橋(01378)成為早市的藍籌最強。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國宏橋官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01378.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國宏橋官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01378.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國宏橋官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早低開419點後反覆尋底，早市中段最低曾見24409點，跌542點，其後開始由谷底反彈，於上午11時半前跌幅已收窄至不足300點；恒指中午收報24727點，跌224點或0.9%，較今早低位跌少逾半。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"中國宏橋官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01378.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國宏橋官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01378.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國宏橋官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"中國鋁業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/02600-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國鋁業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/02600-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國鋁業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"建設銀行官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20230719_FI_source-web_00939-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"建設銀行官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20230719_FI_source-web_00939-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">建設銀行官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：極視角官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260323_FI_source-web_06636.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：極視角官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260323_FI_source-web_06636.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：極視角官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國宏橋官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01378.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國宏橋官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國鋁業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/02600-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國鋁業官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"建設銀行官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20230719_FI_source-web_00939-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">建設銀行官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：極視角官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260323_FI_source-web_06636.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：極視角官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數跑輸大市，半日跌79點或1.66%，報4698點；國企指數跌60點或0.72%，報8393點。主板半日成交1548.28億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指半日跌183點，報24668點，低水60點。科指期貨跌73點，報4687點，低水12點。國指期貨跌49點，報8370點，低水23點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">據報伊朗早前襲擊中東兩處鋁生產設施，其中當地最大鋁生產商阿聯酋環球鋁業公司表示，位於阿布扎比的工廠受到嚴重損毀，引發市場對鋁業供應或更趨緊張的憂慮，導致鋁價今早急升，鋁業股遂成炒作對象。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國宏橋今早全程逆市報升，最高見36.78元，漲6.61%；中午收報35.68元，升幅雖然收窄至3.42%，依然穩坐藍籌升幅榜首。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">板塊內多隻股份同樣炒上，中國鋁業(02600)飆7.86%，報11.66元；南山鋁業(02610)升5.64%，報55.25元；俄鋁(00486)也升3.17%，報4.23元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國鋁業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/02600-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國鋁業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/02600-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國鋁業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金價向上，金礦與金飾零售股再借勢向上。早前公布理想業績的老鋪黃金(06181)，今早成表現次佳藍籌，升2.59%，報633元；紫金礦業(02899)雖然僅微升0.41%，報34.08元，同系紫金黃金國際(02259)則漲2.27%，報175.9元。山東黃金(01787)升3.07%，報32.22元；靈寶黃金(03330)漲6.15%，報26.92元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內銀股亦有份撐市，建設銀行(00939)上周五收市後派成績表，其ADR當晚已高收，該股今早低開高走，開市不久便掉頭倒升，中午收報8.19元，升1.24%；同在上周五收市後公布業績的工商銀行(01398)，股價亦微升0.15%，報6.63元；招商銀行(03968)升0.53%，報49.22元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"建設銀行官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20230719_FI_source-web_00939-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"建設銀行官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20230719_FI_source-web_00939-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">建設銀行官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">不過，重磅股依然跌多於升。兩大藍籌國際金融股早市全程「潛水」，滙控(00005)中午收報122.6元，跌1.76%；友邦(01299)跌0.82%，報84.95元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">「ATMXJ」全線向下，阿里巴巴(09988)半日跌1.88%，報120.3元；騰訊(00700)跌2.23%，報482.4元；美團(03690)跌1.34%，報84.75元；京東(09618)跌0.62%，報113元；小米(01810)跌1.52%，報32.5元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：極視角官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260323_FI_source-web_06636.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：極視角官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260323_FI_source-web_06636.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：極視角官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，今早有4隻新股掛牌，於競價時段雖然互有升跌，但早市全程仍能全體高收。極視角(06636)暫時表現稍為領先，中午收報83.35元，較招股價40元高1.08倍；德適(02526)報202.6元，也較招股價99元高1.05倍；瀚天天成(02726)報102.6元，較招股價76.26元高34.54%；華沿機器人(01021)報19.66元，較招股價17元高15.65%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15811399-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c224%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124727%e9%bb%9e-%e9%8b%81%e6%a5%ad%e6%9d%bf%e5%a1%8a%e7%82%92%e4%b8%8a",
